manifest.name: Send Note
manifest.description: Instantly send a note, to other obsidian users so they can import them into their vault. It uses AWS S3 as a storage backend. Data is shared encrypted by default, and only you and the person you send it to have the key.
manifest.author: Jamie Steiner

data.manifestValue: Instantly send a note, to other obsidian users so they can import them into their vault. It uses AWS S3 as a storage backend. Data is shared encrypted by default, and only you and the person you send it to have the key.
data.communityListValue: Instantly send a note, to other users so they can import them into their vault via URL.
